npm : Is a software registry that contains >800k code packages , it comes with node.js
To install any package do npm install

Here we are creating package.json file
npm init , it will ask few question and will create a package.json file
you can create custom npm run script in scripts section in package.json , to run script type : npm run <script_name>


to use .env install it .

we ignored node_modules we will install the dependecies using npm install 